-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        Project Description
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Urban Transport Simulation

The project contains a main central car. The goal is to go as far as you 
can on the highway without hitting another vehicle. The only other vehicles
present in the highway are cars, buses and trucks. There are up and down 
button that is meant to help navigating the central car to avoid 
collision. There is also the zoom buttons for zooming in and out. Finally, 
there is start and stop button to start and stop the simulation.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        Acknowledgements
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Youtube
2. w3schools.com
3. Lecture materials

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                      What program does
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

The program runs until the central car being navigated collides with 
another vehicle. When this happens, the game stops and a popup shows
game over. The popup has a restart button that allows someone to restart
the game. 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                    Potential bug?
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

None so far.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        Architecture
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------


Inheritance Hierachy :
-----------------------

|-- represents the subclasses of a given  class

Vehicles
    |--Car
    |--Bus
    |--Truck
    |--MyCar

Button
    |--StartButton
    |--StopButton
    |--RestartButton
    |--UpButton
    |--DownButton
    |--ZoomInButton
    |--ZoomOutButton



Aggregation Hierachy :
-----------------------

Simulation
    |--Highway
    |--Vehicle
    |--Mycar
    |--Car
    |--Truck
    |--Bus
    |--Collision
    |--SimulationListener

--------------------------------------------------------------------------


How to run: 
---------------
1. open file on a browser



How to Play:
--------------
1. Use the Up and Down button to move the central vehicle up and down a lane
2. Avoid hitting any vehicle while overtaking
3. You can use start and stop to pause and unpause the simulation